            for a few months.   Eventually coolness will return. 
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-7 col-md-7 col-lg-7">
          <div class="content-item-container about-image-container about-image-container-family">
            <img src="/assets/the_family.jpg" 
              data-original="/assets/the_family.jpg" 
              class="img-responsive js-lazy-load js-lazy-load-immediate" 
              alt="The Family" 
              style="display: block;">
